'''2014年巴西抗议运动'''指为回应[[2014年世界杯足球赛|2014年世界杯足球赛]]及[[2014年世界杯足球赛相关问题|其他问题]]而发生在[[巴西|巴西]]数个城市的民众[[示威|示威]]。

== 背景 ==
抗议活动主要涉及数百亿用在世界杯场馆的雷亚尔公款。早在2013年[[联合会杯|联合会杯]]期间，就曾发生过反对巴西举办杯赛的社会运动<ref name=BBC/>。[[Facebook|Facebook]]群组“反世界杯街头装饰运动”（{{lang-pt|Movimento Anti-Copa de Decoração de Ruas}}）在一个多月的事件获得超过1.5万个“赞”<ref>{{cite news |title= Movimento reúne pichações e arte contra a Copa do Mundo no Brasil |url= http://www.otempo.com.br/cmlink/hotsites/copa-do-mundo-2014/movimento-re%C3%BAne-picha%C3%A7%C3%B5es-e-arte-contra-a-copa-do-mundo-no-brasil-1.856636 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2015-05-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150515162613/http://www.otempo.com.br/cmlink/hotsites/copa-do-mundo-2014/movimento-re%C3%BAne-picha%C3%A7%C3%B5es-e-arte-contra-a-copa-do-mundo-no-brasil-1.856636 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

== 过程 ==
=== 比赛前夕 ===
[[File:Fome_de_bola_02.jpg|thumb]]街头讽刺世界杯支持的[[涂鸦|涂鸦]]]]
2014年1月25日，[[圣保罗|圣保罗]]市中心的示威者与军警发生冲突。根据组织方的[[Twitter|Twitter]]帐号，有108人和28人分别被军警和民警逮捕，入夜前共计128人被捕<ref>{{cite news |title= Grupos protestam pelo Brasil contra a realização da Copa do Mundo |url= http://esportes.estadao.com.br/noticias/futebol,grupos-protestam-pelo-brasil-contra-a-realizacao-da-copa-do-mundo,1122884 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2015-09-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150930164248/http://esportes.estadao.com.br/noticias/futebol,grupos-protestam-pelo-brasil-contra-a-realizacao-da-copa-do-mundo,1122884 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

5月27日，2500名示威者封锁了[[巴西利亚|巴西利亚]]市中心纪念轴附近的街道，造成塞车。示威人群中的300名原住民前往首都抗议原住民用地划界法律的变动。抗议在包括一名骑兵在内的军警被箭头击中结束<ref>{{cite news |title= Protesto contra a Copa termina em confronto com a polícia no DF |url= http://g1.globo.com/distrito-federal/noticia/2014/05/protesto-contra-copa-termina-em-confronto-com-policia-no-df.html |date= 2014-05-27 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2015-05-18 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150518102215/http://g1.globo.com/distrito-federal/noticia/2014/05/protesto-contra-copa-termina-em-confronto-com-policia-no-df.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

5月31日，200名示威者从滨海行政中心前往[[巴西利亚国家体育场|巴西利亚国家体育场]]进行和平示威<ref>{{cite news |title= Protesto contra a Copa do Mundo reúne 200 manifestantes em Brasília |url= http://www.tnonline.com.br/noticias/politica/4,267127,30,05,protesto-contra-a-copa-do-mundo-reune-200-manifestantes-em-brasilia.shtml |date= 2014-05-31 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2014-07-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140714163648/http://tnonline.com.br/noticias/politica/4,267127,30,05,protesto-contra-a-copa-do-mundo-reune-200-manifestantes-em-brasilia.shtml |dead-url= no }}</ref>。翌日，圣保罗军警动用被称为“[[机械战警|机械战警]]”的装甲，专门在世界杯期间保持对抗议活动的控制<ref>{{cite news |title= Protesto contra a Copa reúne 500 pessoas no Centro de São Paulo |url= http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/2014/05/protesto-contra-copa-reune-500-pessoas-no-centro-de-sao-paulo.html |date= 2014-05-31 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2015-02-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150224073946/http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/2014/05/protesto-contra-copa-reune-500-pessoas-no-centro-de-sao-paulo.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

6月3日，[[戈亚尼亚|戈亚尼亚]]有50名抗议者聚集在与{{nft|巴拿马}}举行[[友谊赛|友谊赛]]的{{nft|巴西}}下榻的酒店前。示威者多属于工会和左翼政治团体，纠察队要求为教授和医护人员提供平等的薪水<ref>{{cite news |title= Protesto contra Copa leva confusão à rua de hotel do Brasil |url= http://esportes.terra.com.br/brasil/protesto-contra-copa-reune-30-pessoas-em-hotel-da-selecao,e878c0483e166410VgnVCM3000009af154d0RCRD.html |date= 2014-06-03 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140812022308/http://esportes.terra.com.br/brasil/protesto-contra-copa-reune-30-pessoas-em-hotel-da-selecao%2Ce878c0483e166410VgnVCM3000009af154d0RCRD.html |archivedate= 2014-08-12 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 }}</ref>。

=== 比赛期间 ===
2014年的示威规模总体上比[[联合会杯|联合会杯]]举行的前一年要小，但几乎所有的世界杯比赛举办城市都有示威者和警察爆发冲突。比赛首周，各大城市共有超过20名示威，180人被捕，许多行动引发警方行动<ref>{{cite news |title= Com mais de 20 protestos, 1ª semana de Copa tem 180 detidos em atos |url= http://g1.globo.com/politica/noticia/2014/06/com-mais-de-20-protestos-1-semana-de-copa-tem-180-detidos-em-atos.html |date= 2014-07-19 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2015-07-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150714212238/http://g1.globo.com/politica/noticia/2014/06/com-mais-de-20-protestos-1-semana-de-copa-tem-180-detidos-em-atos.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

6月12日，[[圣保罗|圣保罗]]军警向示威者施放毒气榴弹和橡皮子弹，至少有6人受伤<ref>{{cite news |title= Protestos atraem menos gente, mas voltam a registrar violência |url= http://www.opovo.com.br/app/opovo/politica/2014/06/13/noticiasjornalpolitica,3266301/protestos-atraem-menos-gente-mas-voltam-a-registrar-violencia.shtml |date= 2014-06-13 |access-date= 2015-05-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150715011212/http://www.opovo.com.br/app/opovo/politica/2014/06/13/noticiasjornalpolitica,3266301/protestos-atraem-menos-gente-mas-voltam-a-registrar-violencia.shtml |archive-date= 2015-07-15 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。[[巴西社会民主党|巴西社会民主党]]州长{{link-en|杰拉尔多·阿尔克|Geraldo Alckmin}}为军警的攻击辩护称，警方目的是防止抗议者阻塞通往足球场的主干道<ref>{{cite news |title= Bombas de gás e spray nos olhos: é assim que a polícia reage aos protestos |url= http://brasil.elpais.com/brasil/2014/06/13/politica/1402690293_009379.html |date= 2014-06-13 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2014-08-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140816171115/http://brasil.elpais.com/brasil/2014/06/13/politica/1402690293_009379.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

6月24日在[[阿雷格里港|阿雷格里港]]，约200名示威者聚集在市中心，前往机场。示威人群收到警方监控，一名给一辆汽车的轮胎放气的示威者被捕<ref>{{cite news |title= Protesto contra a Copa reúne mais policiais do que manifestantes |url= http://zh.clicrbs.com.br/rs/porto-alegre/noticia/2014/06/protesto-contra-a-copa-reune-mais-policiais-do-que-manifestantes-4533861.html |date= 2014-06-23 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2015-07-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150714204153/http://zh.clicrbs.com.br/rs/porto-alegre/noticia/2014/06/protesto-contra-a-copa-reune-mais-policiais-do-que-manifestantes-4533861.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

[[File:Manifestação_Copa.webm|thumb]]

6月23日在圣保罗，一名穿着黑色上衣的神秘男子向空中开了三枪，当时警方逮捕了一名示威者。示威者表示，这名男子企图吓跑警察。而警方表示将调查枪手是否属于部队<ref>{{cite news |title= Protesto contra Copa termina com detidos na Avenida Paulista |url= http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/2014/06/protesto-contra-copa-termina-com-detidos-na-avenida-paulista.html |date= 2014-06-23 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2014-08-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140819083532/http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/2014/06/protesto-contra-copa-termina-com-detidos-na-avenida-paulista.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

7月13日世界杯闭幕当天，里约热内卢警方打伤了至少10名俱乐部记者，并发射破片催泪弹。警方包围了300名示威者，阻止他们前往目的地[[马拉卡纳体育场|马拉卡纳体育场]]。军警向[[BBC|BBC]]表示会发布警方滥用内部权力的报告<ref>{{cite news |title= Polícia usa violência em protesto e fere ao menos 10 jornalistas no Rio |url= http://noticias.br.msn.com/brasil/pol%C3%ADcia-usa-viol%C3%AAncia-em-protesto-e-fere-ao-menos-10-jornalistas-no-rio |date= 2014-07-13 |access-date= 2015-05-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140727025523/http://noticias.br.msn.com/brasil/pol%C3%ADcia-usa-viol%C3%AAncia-em-protesto-e-fere-ao-menos-10-jornalistas-no-rio |archive-date= 2014-07-27 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

== 事件 ==
前巴西足球运动员、现政坛人物[[罗马里奥|罗马里奥]]称锦标赛是“历史上最大的盗窃案”，他相信真正的成本超过1000亿里拉（450亿美元）。他呼吁深入调查被普遍滥用的公共基金，确定这时抗议活动持续的原因<ref>{{cite news |title= Romário diz que Copa de 2014 será o 'maior roubo da história' |url= http://oglobo.globo.com/esportes/romario-diz-que-copa-de-2014-sera-maior-roubo-da-historia-4345965 |date= 2014-06-13 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2014-07-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140719220045/http://oglobo.globo.com/esportes/romario-diz-que-copa-de-2014-sera-maior-roubo-da-historia-4345965 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title= Copa será o maior roubo da história |url= http://diariodonordeste.verdesmares.com.br/cadernos/nacional/romario-copa-sera-o-maior-roubo-da-historia-1.303877 |date= 2014-06-13 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2014-07-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140714185300/http://diariodonordeste.verdesmares.com.br/cadernos/nacional/romario-copa-sera-o-maior-roubo-da-historia-1.303877 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title="Copa do Mundo vai custar R$ 100 bilhões para o Brasil", diz Romário|url=http://esportes.r7.com/futebol/noticias/-copa-do-mundo-vai-custar-r-100-bilhoes-para-o-brasil-diz-romario-20110622.html|date=2014-06-13|access-date=2015-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714223244/http://esportes.r7.com/futebol/noticias/-copa-do-mundo-vai-custar-r-100-bilhoes-para-o-brasil-diz-romario-20110622.html|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title= Romário diz ao R7 que Brasil vai gastar R$ 100 bilhões na Copa |url= http://rederecord.r7.com/video/romario-diz-ao-r7-que-brasil-vai-gastar-r-100-bilhoes-na-copa-4e028547b51a4b961b36b283/ |date= 2014-06-13 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20141020214352/http://rederecord.r7.com/video/romario-diz-ao-r7-que-brasil-vai-gastar-r-100-bilhoes-na-copa-4e028547b51a4b961b36b283/ |archivedate= 2014-10-20 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title= Romário volta a criticar organização da Copa: "o Brasil perdeu de goleada" |url= http://copadomundo.uol.com.br/noticias/redacao/2014/03/18/romario-volta-a-criticar-organizacao-da-copa-o-brasil-perdeu-de-goleada.htm |date= 2014-06-13 |accessdate= 2015-05-09 |archive-date= 2014-07-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140714114509/http://copadomundo.uol.com.br/noticias/redacao/2014/03/18/romario-volta-a-criticar-organizacao-da-copa-o-brasil-perdeu-de-goleada.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

6月12日揭幕战开赛前，圣保罗和里约热内卢等数个城市的警方与示威者爆发冲突。圣保罗警方动用了催泪瓦斯<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-27811657|title=Brazil World Cup: Clashes at Sao Paulo and Rio protests|date=2014-06-12|work=BBC News|accessdate=2014-06-13|archive-date=2014-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613023706/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-27811657|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/12/anti-world-cup-protests-brazilian-cities-sao-paulo-rio-de-janeiro|title=Anti-World Cup protests in Brazilian cities mark countdown to kick-off|date=2014-06-12|work=Guardian|accessdate=2014-06-13|archive-date=2014-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613044647/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/12/anti-world-cup-protests-brazilian-cities-sao-paulo-rio-de-janeiro|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2656102/Brazil-gets-ready-greatest-Earth-just-dont-mention-poor-pitches-subway-strikes-protests-hackers.html|title=Brazilian protesters angry at the cost of the World Cup set fires in the streets and clash violently with riot police hours before opening match in Sao Paulo|date=2014-06-12|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2014-06-13|archive-date=2014-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612131719/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2656102/Brazil-gets-ready-greatest-Earth-just-dont-mention-poor-pitches-subway-strikes-protests-hackers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6月12日，[[CNN|CNN]]记者沙斯塔·达林顿和制片人芭芭拉·奥凡尼提迪斯报道抗议时受伤。两人报道防暴武器被滥用时，[[催泪瓦斯|催泪瓦斯]]弹直接打在芭芭拉的手腕上<ref>{{cite news |title=CNN producer left bloodied after trouble breaks out on day one in Brazil |url=https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/blogs/the-rio-report/cnn-reporters-left-bloodied-trouble-breaks-day-one-135909960.html |date=2014-06-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714210544/https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/blogs/the-rio-report/cnn-reporters-left-bloodied-trouble-breaks-day-one-135909960.html |archivedate=2014-07-14 |accessdate=2015-05-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Brazilian police fire tear gas at World Cup protesters; CNN employees injured by anti-riot weapons|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/06/12/world/americas/brazil-world-cup-protests/|date=2014-06-12|accessdate=2015-05-09|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704210719/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/06/12/world/americas/brazil-world-cup-protests/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Sao Paulo violent protests on World Cup opening day as journalist 'injured' amid rubber bullets and stun grenades|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/southamerica/brazil/10895328/Sao-Paulo-violent-protests-on-World-Cup-opening-day-as-journalist-injured-amid-rubber-bullets-and-stun-grenades.html|date=2014-06-12|accessdate=2015-05-09|archive-date=2014-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703102905/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/southamerica/brazil/10895328/Sao-Paulo-violent-protests-on-World-Cup-opening-day-as-journalist-injured-amid-rubber-bullets-and-stun-grenades.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

